{"word":"H982 - בָּטַח - bâṭach - baw-takh' - Be bold - தைரியமாயிரு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּטַח"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâṭach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-takh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be bold / தைரியமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நம்பு, நம்பியிரு, நம்பிக்கை வைத்திரு, நம்பிக்கையாயிரு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to trust"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to trust, to trust in"},{"paragraph":"2) to have confidence, to be confident"},{"paragraph":"3) to be bold"},{"paragraph":"4) to be secure"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil) to cause to trust, to make secure"},{"paragraph":"2) to feel safe, to be careless"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>hie</i> for refuge (but not so <i>precipitately</i> as <a href=\"#/H2620 - חָסָה - châçâh - khaw-saw'/2620\">H2620</a>); figuratively to <i>trust</i>, be <i>confident</i> or <i>sure: - </i>be bold (confident, secure, sure), careless (one, woman), put confidence, (make to) hope, (put, make to) trust."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4009 - מִבְטָח - mibṭâch - mib-tawkh'/4009\">H4009</a>, <a href=\"#/H982 - בָּטַח - bâṭach - baw-takh'/982\">H982</a>, <a href=\"#/H983 - בֶּטַח - beṭach - beh'takh/983\">H983</a>, <a href=\"#/H984 - בֶּטַח - Beṭach - beh'takh/984\">H984</a>, <a href=\"#/H985 - בִּטְחָה - biṭchâh - bit-khaw'/985\">H985</a>, <a href=\"#/H986 - בִּטָּחֹון - biṭṭâchôwn - bit-taw-khone'/986\">H986</a>, <a href=\"#/H987 - בַּטֻּחֹות - baṭṭuchôwth - bat-too-khoth'/987\">H987</a>"}]}